outputs.output_descr: This project fulfilled the priority needs of the Palestinian Authority to construct a  Governmental Hospital in the Salfeet District. The hospital provides emergency room, in patient, maternity, general surgery, lab, pharmacy, pediatric, and other services to the general public.
